patterns.name: meta.definition.destructor.d
patterns.begin:
(?x)
    				(?:  ^                                 # begin-of-line
    				  |  (?: (?<!else|new|=) )             #  or word + space before name
    				)
					((?:\b(?:public|private|protected|static|final|synchronized|abstract|export)\b\s*)*) # modifier
    				(~this) # actual name
    				 \s*(\()                           # start bracket or end-of-line
